content:
i don’t know your particular circumstance, but ill ask you what are you trying to gain in grasping your thought? 

surely in this grasping you are attempting to move from the perception that ‘i am arrogant’ to ‘i am not arrogant’. but in attempting to move away, you are actually distorting your perception of what you are. so why do you have emotional goals at all? what do you think you are doing that is beneficial to your circumstance? dont take any conclusion and keep going
